Weight: 0.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/ears.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/cleric/armour/ears.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/armour/ears.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/enchanter/armour/ears.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/ears.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/ears.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/ears.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/ears.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/ears.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/ears.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/ears.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/shaman/armour/ears.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/ears.shtml">WAR</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/ears.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) <BR>
(STR +5) </font>
