<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Do be careful when master looting sarnaks.  I got one in Burning Woods, where I'd been master looting for five or six consecutive days, off a Sarnak Extremist.  It looks exactly like a mithril amulet (chrysoberyl talisman icon), which drops in places like BW with relative frequency.  After so much time, I'd forgotten entirely about earrings of station.  I just looted it.  Thankfully, I was with an enchanter and mage, so I didn't upset anyone!</font></td></tr></table>
