<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Cambyses</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-11-19 03:47:09</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>ok guys get ready for this.I would say that the best place to get the Station earring is in Overthere.Its a place called the tower.Sarnaks spawn there (Knights,2 types of Casters and Berz with whips for dack race quest)the earrings drop off CASTERS ONLY!!or thats what i have seen them drop off so far.They are very rare drops but i got lucky and had 2 drop in less then 30 mins.to get to the Tower...i dont know the Overthere zone very well but i know this for a fact. Coming from FM you should go pu till you hit a road thing or a trail, go right from there and follow the trail or road till you see a tower thing DO NOT GO IN THE TOWER there will be 4 to 5 spawns in there.You should shout firts to see if tower is camped if so then jsut wait if you really want the earrings and its worth it good exp and good loot.Most of the time you will have to group it is safer this way too.If you come from Warslike you would take the road to the left and you will still see the tower.<BR>
I hope this helps you out the earring dose drop in Lake of ill omen and FM and any other place were there are Sarnak casters.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Cambyses,<BR>
35 Warrior of the Grudge Bearer<BR>
FENNIN RO</font></td></tr></table>
